=================
The CrateDB Shell
=================

.. image:: https://github.com/crate/crash/workflows/test/badge.svg
    :target: https://github.com/crate/crash/actions
    :alt: Outcome of CI

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/crash.svg
